      "widgets_values": [
        "# ComfyUI Escape Codes - Text Road & Text\n\n## Line Breaks & Spaces\n\n| Code | Result | Usage |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| `\\n` | 1 line break | Move to next line |\n| `\\n\\n` | 2 line breaks | Create paragraph (blank line) |\n| `\\n\\n\\n` | 3 line breaks | Wider spacing |\n| `\\t` | Tab | Indent text |\n| `\\t\\t` | Double tab | Double indentation |\n| ` ` (space) | Single space | Add a space |\n| `  ` (2 spaces) | Double space | Double spacing |\n\n---\n\n## Special Characters & Punctuation\n\n| Code | Result | Usage |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| `\\-` | Hyphen/Dash | List items |\n| `\\*` | Asterisk | Emphasis or bullets |\n| `\\\\` | Backslash | Display a backslash |\n| `\\\"` | Double quotes | Embed quotes |\n| `\\'` | Apostrophe | Embed apostrophe |\n| `\\|` | Pipe/Vertical bar | Separator |\n| `\\#` | Hash/Pound | Avoid markdown interpretation |\n\n---\n\n## Text Formatting (if supported)\n\n| Code | Result | Usage |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| `**text**` | **Bold text** (Markdown) | Strong emphasis |\n| `*text*` | *Italic text* (Markdown) | Light emphasis |\n| `~~text~~` | ~~Strikethrough~~ (Markdown) | Deleted text |\n| `` ` `` | `Inline code` | Code block |\n\n---\n\n## Practical Combinations for Text Road\n\n| Use Case | Code | Example |\n|----------|------|---------|\n| Separate 2 prompts | `\\n\\n` | prompt1\\n\\nprompt2 |\n| Bullet list | `\\n\\-` | item1\\n\\-item2 |\n| Numbered paragraphs | `\\n\\n1. ` | text\\n\\n1. item1\\n\\n2. item2 |\n| Dash enumeration | `\\n\\- ` | text\\n\\- item1\\n\\- item2 |\n| Indented list | `\\t\\- ` | \\t\\- sub-item |\n| Double line spacing | `\\n\\n\\t` | For elegant formatting |\n\n---\n\n## Text Road Configuration Examples\n\n### Example 1: Prompts separated by double break\n```\nSeparator: \\n\\n\n```\n**Result:**\n```\nprompt1\n\nprompt2\n\nprompt3\n```\n\n### Example 2: Bullet list\n```\nPrefix: \\n\\- \nSeparator: \\n\\- \nSuffix: (empty)\n```\n**Result:**\n```\n- item1\n- item2\n- item3\n```\n\n### Example 3: Indented paragraphs\n```\nPrefix: \\n\\t\nSeparator: \\n\\n\n```\n**Result:**\n```\n\ttext1\n\n\ttext2\n```\n\n### Example 4: Numbered format\n```\nPrefix: \\n1. \nSeparator: \\n2. \n(add suffix to close)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Important Notes\n\n⚠️ **Escaping in Python (if using in PyCodeMax):**\n- Pure Python: `\\n` works directly\n- Raw string: `r\"\\n\"` displays literally as `\\n`\n- Double backslash: `\"\\\\n\"` = backslash + n\n\n✅ **ComfyUI Text Road** interprets `\\n` correctly in text fields\n\n📌 **Tip**: Test different combinations by adding a **Show Text** node to visualize the exact result before use"
      ],
